to having their opinions changed

00:09:13.511 --> 00:09:14.971 position:50% align:center line:84%
are identified.

00:09:15.055 --> 00:09:17.766 position:50% align:center line:84%
- We target them
with the information database

00:09:17.849 --> 00:09:20.435 position:50% align:center line:84%
and use excessive
personalized ads

00:09:20.518 --> 00:09:23.104 position:50% align:center line:84%
