Insanity
can be spread instantly.

00:09:33.448 --> 00:09:35.825 position:50% align:center line:84%
- I know that's happened
in North America.

00:09:35.909 --> 00:09:38.745 position:50% align:center line:84%
Although there's no guarantee
the same algorithm

00:09:38.828 --> 00:09:40.789 position:50% align:center line:84%
